hopobject.body: Do you know the address? purecare celliant pillow protector In fact, the example of the last bubble is instructive. The housing boom created many high-paying jobs, a lot of them the kind you can do without a college degree. Unfortunately the demand for those houses, partly created by very low interest rates, was false. In the end, much economic damage was done by capital and labor being pulled into housing only to be unceremoniously dumped later.
